                          ->Sequences : 1.string,2.tuple,3.list,4.range
                          ->Sets : it is a unordered collection of elements.(not supports indexing)
                          ->Mapping/Dictionaries : it works acc. to (key:value) pair.
          type(a) :- this gives the datype of variable a.
